title: Ansell AlphaTec 37-310, Multipurpose Nitrile Gloves, Reusable Kitchen Gloves, Latex Free Gloves with Chemical Protection, Cooking and Cleaning Gloves, Blue Nitrile Gloves Medium, 12 Pairs
features: SILICONE & LATEX FREE GLOVES – These nitrile gloves are perfect silicone and latex free gloves for sensitive skin. Use them as cleaning gloves or kitchen gloves without the risk of type 1 allergies, ensuring comfort and protection

IDEAL FOR CLEANING & FOOD PREP – Ansell's nitrile gloves medium serve as cleaning gloves and kitchen gloves These durable latex free gloves are designed to handle aggressive chemicals, hot liquids, and greasy substances providing safety and comfort

LIGHT CHEMICAL PROTECTION – The nitrile gloves medium are latex free gloves that use NBR material for reliable protection against light acids, greases, oils, and liquid splashes Ideal as kitchen gloves and cleaning gloves offering safety and dexterity

THICKNESS AND PRECISION – The 8mil thickness of these nitrile gloves ensures precision, accuracy, and grip in various environments Use these latex free gloves as kitchen gloves or cleaning gloves for enhanced performance

130 YEARS OF PROTECTION: For over 130 years, Ansell, Australia’s top safety solutions provider, has delivered durable protection in tough environments Explore our nitrile gloves, in various sizes and lengths, at the Ansell brand store for industry-leading safety solutions
